          "candidate_value": "and after Nov 26, 2010 Royal Trust Accounts Royal Trust Alliance Plan \u00ae including linked accounts 4 Royal Trust T-Bills Savings \u00ae Royal Trust Daily Interest Savings \u00ae Royal Trust Daily Interest Chequing \u00ae Royal Trust US Daily Interest \u00ae If you have any questions about today's rat",
