          "evidence_chunk_id": "chunk-b32cb1a86d84e365",
          "evidence_text_excerpt": "and after Nov 26, 2010\nRoyal Trust Accounts\nRoyal Trust Alliance Plan \u00ae including linked accounts 4\nRoyal Trust T-Bills Savings \u00ae\nRoyal Trust Daily Interest Savings \u00ae\nRoyal Trust Daily Interest Chequing \u00ae\nRoyal Trust US Daily Interest \u00ae\nIf you have any questions about today's rates, please visit your local branch or call us at 1 \n 800 769-2511 .\nNOTES\nP \u00a0 Denotes interest is calculated at this rate on the applicable portion of the daily closing credit \n account balance.\n1 VIP means the account is linked to an RBC VIP \n Banking package.\n2 PRF means the account is linked to a RateLink \n Preference package.\n3 PRI means the account is linked to a Private \n Banking package.\n4 Canadian dollar linked accounts that are non-interest bearing do not pay interest.\n5 Only Canadian dollar personal deposit accounts can be linked.\nInterest rates are subject to change without notice at any time.",
