          "evidence_text_excerpt": "nthly fee rebate legal bug 2 and Avion points earn rate legal bug 1 will not be impacted until the next calendar month, which is when we will re-evaluate whether you\u2019re still eligible to receive a monthly fee rebate and if your points earn rate should be modified.\nThrough the Value Program , Avion points legal bug 1 are calculated monthly and take into account all in-store and online debit purchases from, and returns to, an enrolled account.\nFor example, say you purchase a $300 blender on debit in December and receive your Avion points. In January, you return the blender and get a $300 credit to your bank account, but you also make $500 in debit purchases. For January, you would be awarded points for $200 of your debit spend ($500 in debit purchases minus the $300 return). Alternatively, if in January you do not make any debit purchases (or spend less than $300) and only return the $300",
